content_text: I wake up early in the morning around 7:00 AM, then I get an freshen up. After that I go to the gym, an exercise for around 1 1/2 hours. Then I came back to home and get ready for the office. Then I commute through my personal vehicle to the office traveling for around 40 kilometers. Then I work around 9 1/2 hours and take breaks in between for lunch. Then in the evening I came back to home and spend some time with my family and friends and I go to sleep early.
